Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:06.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(236,400)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.62,0:01:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.04,0:01:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快帮我解脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just put me out of me misery
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.66,0:01:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多美好的一天  哪里会出错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could be wrong on such a fine day?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.75,0:01:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.89,0:01:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天才不好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's not the day for that word, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.21,0:01:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我收到了煎炸厨师工会的信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:18.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not after I received this letter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the fry cooks' union
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.10,0:01:23.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面写  煎炸厨师海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:23.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says here: "Fry cook, SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.74,0:01:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,积攒过多假期未放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has accumulated too much vacation time"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是再不休假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if you don't take some time off
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就会被罚款了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to pay a fine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.47,0:01:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time off?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.19,0:01:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来没办法更委婉地说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess there's just no other way to say this
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  放大假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, take a vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.99,0:01:40.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:40.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.15,0:01:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比我想象的还要顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that went better than I expected
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了  要放大假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready, vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了  要放大假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready, vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.85,0:01:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放大假  放大假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vacation, vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我提早回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am home early
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放大假了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, good night, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放大假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:07.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1112,520)}海草哥麦片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  蟹堡王的员工们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Krusty crew
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And hello, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为你去放大假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you were on vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在也还在放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was, and is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是叫你去放大假了吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you to take a vacation, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么是放大假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's a vacation?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.17,0:02:32.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放大假就是不用来上班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:32.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, a vacation is when you don't come in to work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.74,0:02:33.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不上班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:33.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我整天要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What will I do all day?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去玩什么的  反正不关我事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just go, have fun or whatever, I really don't care
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之不能来这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just can't be here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.12,0:02:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我走了  谁来煎肉饼清理烤架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But who will fry the patties
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and clean the grill while I'm gone?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥自己没办法搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward can't do it all alone
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我更不去搞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nor will I
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我才雇了个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why I've hired
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.65,0:02:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无薪实习生来临时帮你代班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an unpaid intern as your temporary replacement
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, boss
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好第一天上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready for my first day
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.29,0:02:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说海星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speaking of starfish
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,代班到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here's your replacement right here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,代班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Replacement?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少插科打诨害我赔钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough banter on my dime
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.82,0:03:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boss
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班得要有正确的工具才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll need the right tools for the job
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.05,0:03:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这挠肚子器上还放了个小小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They put a tiny me in this belly-scratcher
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竟然还能挠背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It scratches backs, too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来交给我吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take it from here, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just go on home
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开开心心放大假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真得给派大星示范一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really should show Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正确的翻肉饼技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the proper patty- flipping technique
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放大假了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on vacation, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能回去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not allowed to go to work
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的胃都瘪下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My stomach has receded
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板不让我到蟹堡王上班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krab said I couldn't work at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又没不让我过去吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He didn't say I couldn't eat there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我回去的门票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my ticket back inside
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你毁了我的假期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ruining my vacation--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我没法远离你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是来看你的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not here to see you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  非得再那样闹一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, do we have to go through this again?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.45,0:04:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我过来是当客人  不是来上班的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here as a customer, not an employee
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是找派大星买个蟹黄堡当午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just going to grab a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with Patrick for lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  但是只准吃午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, but lunch only
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是敢碰一下锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you so much as touch a spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就滚戴维琼斯柜子放大假去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll be vacationing in Davy Jones's locker
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have my word, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不上班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No working
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  来吃午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pat, it's time for your lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可以那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要把烤架的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to turn up the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.58,0:04:36.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,调到整整298华氏度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:36.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to exactly 298 degrees Fahrenheit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:36.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fnArial\pos(846,920)}147.78{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}摄氏度
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不能这样糟蹋蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, this is no way to treat a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班的事  我跟你怎么交代的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you about working?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.09,0:04:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.91,0:04:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出去  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out you go, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我的知识可以帮派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But my knowledge could help Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,维持蟹堡王的高水准
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maintain the high standard of the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边的一切我们都能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got it all under control here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假没放完  就别让我看到你人影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see hide nor tail of you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until your vacation is over
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got that?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, boy, off you go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没放完就别回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't come back until it's over
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道有什么能让我振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know just the thing to get the spirits up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,官方正版蟹堡王玩具套装
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The official Krusty Krab play set
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.04,0:05:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  请马上来二十份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I need 20 Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the double, please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Mr. Squidward, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十份蟹黄堡马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,20 Krabby Patties coming up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在里面干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再不把你方屁股挪回家  我会亏钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to cost me some loot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you don't get your square keister home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out, out, out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放完假再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until your vacation is over
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放这无聊的大假能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What to do on this boring vacation?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道有什么能让我振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know just the thing to get the old spirits up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请来二十份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need 20 Krabby Patties, please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  老兄弟老章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, old buddy, old squid
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十份蟹黄堡马上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,20 Krabby Patties coming
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.77,0:06:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放假老想着蟹堡王  确实不健康
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is unhealthy to think about the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I'm on vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得出门走走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to get out of the house
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  他又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, he's out there again
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  你踏入了蟹堡王的领地了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, you're on Krusty Krab property
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back it up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:27.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(190,716)}入口
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.32,0:06:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.07,0:06:27.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:27.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Further
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,578)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想开心放假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In order to enjoy my vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.75,0:06:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得身心都远离工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to stay away from work, physically and mentally
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这倒让我想起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That reminds me of
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我慢着  工作狂宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, Mr. WorkaholicPants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是在放假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.51,0:06:58.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得坐好放松
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:58.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to just sit down and relax
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's more like it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐好看云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just sit back and watch the clouds
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那朵像水母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one's a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.91,0:07:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那朵像海盗船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a pirate ship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(406,232)}少盐番茄酱
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那朵像少盐番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's a low-salt ketchup
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少盐番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Low-salt ketchup?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热腾腾的面包送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got your steaming hot bun delivery here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the big idea here?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.77,0:07:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(768,452)}卫生间
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道自己有耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know I had an ear
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个我刚清理过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just cleaned that one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.27,0:07:58.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:58.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它会讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It talks
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.85,0:08:03.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:03.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody help
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.94,0:08:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王  你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune, it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有点进退两难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in a bit of a fix here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.05,0:08:11.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:11.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.58,0:08:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天受够你了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Had enough for one day, son
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你开船送我回家  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ride home, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a problem at all, me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个路口右转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take the next right
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  都开过路口了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, we just passed the turnoff
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家在后面那个方向  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My house is back that way, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远了去了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Far out, little man
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远了去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Far out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说要带我去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did you say you were taking me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, boy--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我带了你锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought your spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.93,0:09:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.67,0:09:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come on
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.12,0:09:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快拿啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get the spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开心放大假去吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your vacation, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not fair
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.26,0:09:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板干嘛要费尽气力赶走我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would Mr. Krabs try so hard to get rid of me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是放个假而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm only on vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.77,0:09:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's a
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远放不完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,permanent vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.95,0:09:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.15,0:09:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板要找人替代我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs wants to replace me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have known
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星一直都眼红我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's had his eye on my job all along
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一直都在密谋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's been scheming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害别人以为我过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They think I'm outdated
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害别人以为我完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They think I'm all washed up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就见识给别人看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll show them
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到蟹堡王上班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Working at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整天做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flipping Krabby Patties all day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flipping Krusty Krab--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,working
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,堡蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patties Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这首歌好难记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a hard song to remember
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们以为自己谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who do they think they are?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给蟹堡王奉献了大好年华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've given the best years of my life to this place
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果蟹堡王的人却想把我当垃圾开除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they think they can just fire me like that, like trash?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.55,0:10:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.85,0:10:10.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:10.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.06,0:10:12.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:12.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直在等你呢  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you're scaring me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty, please
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One shell on a shingle
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.16,0:10:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你的厨艺提升了一千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're cooking's improved one-thousandfold
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总算掌握诀窍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You finally got the hang of it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No wonder
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星一小时可做不出那么多蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick could never flip that many patties in an hour
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那家伙是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to that feller anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫他待家里看电视了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told him to stay home and watch television
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么那么做  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do it, laddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.40,0:11:11.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太爱蟹堡王的臭油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:11.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love the putrid grease of the Krusty Krab so much
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就走不开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't stay away
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不用走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你积攒的假已经放完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your accumulated vacation time is used up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工会再也没法罚我款了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The union can't fine me anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定省下了不少钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must have saved a fortune
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bumping Barnacle, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there she is
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比我一年赚到的还多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's more than I make in a year
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别找我加工资
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be asking me for a raise
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yippee
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.33,0:11:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我欣然接受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I happily acquiesce
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.89,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&}假发潮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:45.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(245.316,450)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:45.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(495.678,728)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:47.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(407.566,442)\frz29.52}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(533.736,694)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(421.602,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.57,0:12:00.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  这一定会是我们最棒的巡演了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:12:00.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, this is going to be our most rocking tour ever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟们  看我的新造型首次登场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, dudes, check out the debut of my new look
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你头上那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that on your head?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  那是假发还是一叠厕纸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, is that a wig or a pile of toilet paper?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.01,0:12:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  给个机会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys, give it a chance
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我试戴一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try it on
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我反光的秃头露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've revealed my shiny dome
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烫手山芋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot potato
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.18,0:12:20.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:20.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Catch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it back, man
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.92,0:12:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要就去接啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want it, you got to catch it, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.81,0:12:27.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:27.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, man
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我漂亮的假发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My beautiful wig
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,176)}垃圾场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686,928)}垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,366)}假发公墓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(902,542)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.20,0:12:48.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:48.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm read
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卷卷的长发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curly tresses?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓬蓬的质感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poofy texture?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痒痒的头皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Itchy scalp?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是顶假发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a wig
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我新造型怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you like my new look?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要救你脱离那个吃脑子的外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm saving you from that brain-eating alien
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它还在袭击你脑袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's attacking your head
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  唯一袭击我的东西就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, the only thing attacking me is you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.31,0:13:22.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:22.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.93,0:13:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.17,0:13:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为你头上戴的是新型棉花糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a new type of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cotton candy you wear on your head
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是  不过那点子很有创意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not, but that is an excellent idea
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.77,0:13:36.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:36.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.51,0:13:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的新造型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my new look
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我戴了顶假发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing a wig
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wig?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我憋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我憋不住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't stand
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不觉得那有点傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's a little silly?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, man
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.45,0:14:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我每周泡调味澡的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for my weekly condiment soak
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(234,634)}芥末
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦回避一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice wig
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.64,0:14:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天可时髦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am very fashionable today
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时髦宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Square Fashion
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时装不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice couture
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发型不错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice 'do, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.05,0:14:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.65,0:14:29.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以上哪做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:29.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where can I get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(208,368)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那假发跟你也太搭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wig really suits you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:45.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,324)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,何人何事何地何时何因何法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who, what, wher, when, why, how?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意到我今天哪不一样没  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Notice anything different about me today, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我戴了顶假发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing a wig
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会没注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could I have missed it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能相信这是我在马路上捡到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you believe I found it lying around in the street?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.76,0:15:06.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要的话  下班后就去给你捡假发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want to, after work
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we could go look for a wig for you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发出动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wig away
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.18,0:15:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这上过了一堆垃圾食品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've served a lot of junk here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这头发堡根本不能忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but a hair patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.04,0:15:38.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你头上戴了什么鬼东西  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:38.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in Davy Jones' locker is on your head, son?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑袋戴了顶新假发  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my new wig, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.09,0:15:41.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:41.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, take it off
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头发都掉进蟹黄堡里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The hair's getting into the patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摘下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it off?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不能摘  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can't, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.55,0:15:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的假发给大家带来了快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wig makes everyone so happy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.15,0:15:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自从我戴上了假发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever since I began wearing it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到的每个人脸上洋溢着笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everyone I see gets a big grin on their face
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想象得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can imagine
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我留着假发吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please let me keep it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是假发对你意义这么大  那就留吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it means that much to you, you can keep it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是必须得戴发网
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you've got to wear a hairnet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是再让我看到蟹黄堡里有头发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, if I see one more hairy patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就把你假发丢进垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your wig goes in the Dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好要练空手道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for karate practice?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看得出来你注意到了我的新假发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you've noticed my new wig
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很棒  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's great, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad you like it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待会儿见  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.55,0:16:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两份蟹黄堡  加帅气当配菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two Krabby Patties and a side order of lookin' good
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice wig
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喜欢维持造型是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like to keep in style, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去见女王了吗  呆子王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Off to meet the queen, Sir Nerd Leroy?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.95,0:16:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The name is SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我并没要去见皇室成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and no, I am not meeting royalty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.36,0:16:49.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定是说我打扮得像皇室成员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:49.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be referring to my regal appearance
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家说的好话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for your kind words
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.62,0:16:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望能把这么棒的假发献给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I could give you such nice wigs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要稍微给你头发剪短一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a little off the top?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你假发大到可以绕着人走一圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, your wig's big enough to go around
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't good
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.57,0:17:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都开始嫉妒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone's getting jealous
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我要藏厨房里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, I'll be hiding in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有事就进来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you need me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藏好你的丑态  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide your shame, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.23,0:17:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,藏好你的丑态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide your shame
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:18.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(306,498)}大人物唱片
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尼德针鱼乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ned and the Needlefish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.14,0:17:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.93,0:17:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.23,0:17:23.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去问那边那位秃头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:23.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask Baldy McBaldyson over here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尼德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ned
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.67,0:17:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太顺利了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good going, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又不是故意没头发的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't help not having hair
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.69,0:17:32.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们成立这个乐队有且仅有一个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We formed this band
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it was for one reason and one reason only
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是赚大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To make a lot of money
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果你没了头发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you not having hair
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我们赚不到钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is getting in the way of that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们卖的是唱片  不是假牙牙膏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are selling records, not denture cream
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要么你带着头发回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Either you come back with hair
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要么就别回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or don't come back at all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:43.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878,722)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙儿回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to go home, boys
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878,722)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快拖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost finished
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还很实用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's functional, too
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟你脑子一样中用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about as functional as your brain
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.86,0:17:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:17:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没在夸你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a compliment
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整个裤头村都在笑你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The entire town is laughing at you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, handsome
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你脑袋是你以前的两倍大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, your head is twice as large as before
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never been tall before
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那顶假发染上了寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wig is infested with parasites
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That tickles
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来你样子有多可笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see how ridiculous you look?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得样子挺酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think that it looks cool
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算我把你锁冰库里  你也不懂酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't know cool if I locked you in the freezer
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提醒你一下  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For your information, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥以前把我锁冰库里过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward has locked me in the freezer
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我知道什么叫酷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I think I know what cool is
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后别戴那顶脏东西来上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stop wearing that nasty thing to work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No "buts"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我假发和屁股都不能戴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I can't have a wig or a butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.37,注释,,0,0,0,,[ butt（屁股）与 but（但是）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是  不把假发扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means, until you get rid of that wig
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就给我拍屁股走人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get your butt out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨天我一直没机会跟海绵宝宝谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never got a chance to talk to SpongeBob yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我笑得太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was laughing too hard
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.20,0:19:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.42,0:19:10.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:10.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,688)}礁石影院\N\N正在上映\N美发淑女
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为什么得把假发扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would I want to get rid of my wig?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看它给大家带来了多少欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look how happy it makes everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它确实引来了不少注意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it does attract a lot of attention
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.04,0:19:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家的目光就是离不开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People just can't keep their eyes off of me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(330,262)}美发淑女
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的也一样  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neither can I, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.05,0:19:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true, Tom
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是我真正的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this isn't my real hair
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I stole it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.10,0:19:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.15,0:19:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.03,0:19:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发给我缓冲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The wig broke my fall
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆米花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Popcorn
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总能站出来挺我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You always come through for me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  能消停会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, do you mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.74,0:19:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看电影讲话很没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's very rude to talk during a movie
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也是  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You too, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家还想看电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are trying to watch the movie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪能看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, they can't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好  你的破假发把银幕都挡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, your stupid wig is blocking the whole screen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摘下来  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it off, jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down in front
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.90,0:20:12.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:12.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take the wig off
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  把注意力放回到电影上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People, return your attention to the movie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我的假发迷人又欢欣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know my wig is glamorous and exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但根本就没必要挑起暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but there is no need to start a riot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.47,0:20:24.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来挑起暴动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start a riot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就说那部是烂片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you that movie was terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在明白我说的话了吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now do you see what I'm saying, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.38,0:20:37.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得很对  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:37.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发给我自己带来了不少快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got so much enjoyment out of the wig myself
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为它也会给别人快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I assumed everyone else did, too
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候坚强一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to be strong
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想跟你说清楚讲明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want you to know that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽管我认识你才几天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even though I didn't know you existed a few days ago
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也无法想象没有你的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine life without you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快一点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论别人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter what they say
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你对我而言  永远都很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll always be cool to me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不会戴配饰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never accessorize again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做出了正确的事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did the right thing, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.91,0:21:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得上哪去找头发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I going to get some hair?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的事业毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My career is ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.02,0:21:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的假发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wig
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Victory is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.65,0:21:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wigs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.39,0:21:55.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都是假发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:55.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wigs, wigs, they're everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他有你的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got your hair
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.16,0:21:59.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:21:59.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.14,0:22:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.32,0:22:03.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码他没戴假发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least he's not wearing a wig
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.02,0:22:04.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看我的新假发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:04.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at my new wig
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.83,0:22:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家全都戴着假发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone's wearing wigs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.87,0:22:07.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都戴着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:07.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.75,0:22:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我开始觉得自己有点被背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel a little betrayed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.29,0:22:11.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你昨天还取笑过我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:11.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You made fun of me yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.94,0:22:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发套明明不酷才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought powdered wigs were uncool
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.65,0:22:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前确实不酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they were
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.22,0:22:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But look
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(994,198)}尼德针鱼乐队
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.67,0:22:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尼德针鱼乐队戴着我的假发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ned and the Needlefish wearing my wig
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.00,0:22:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我抢先酷了一把吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I was cool before anyone else?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.07,0:22:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you were
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.53,0:22:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但再也没这回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But not anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.88,0:22:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.62,0:22:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望我有顶假发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a wig
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.40,0:22:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别难过了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be sad, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.05,0:22:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以找我借啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can borrow one of mine
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.31,0:22:39.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还之前先洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:39.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just wash it before you return it
